Given this political fundraising email, respond with the name of the committee in the disclaimer that begins with Paid for by but does not include Paid for by, the committee address or the treasurer name. If no committee is present, return "None". Do not include any other text, no yapping.
name: Team Kean
email: info@outreach.tomkean.com
subject: RE: Shifting gears
body: Friend—Election month is HERE! We are now only FOUR short days away from oneof the most historic elections of our lifetime. This is THE final stretch…themoment we have been building and working toward… and we need your help ONELAST TIME to finish strong. HELP KEAN FINISH STRONG We are about to shift ourremaining resources into an ALL OUT Get Out The Vote Operation—will you pitchin one last time to magnify our efforts? This is our final push to keep Tom’sads running throughout the district, reach every single voter with Tom’sunifying message, and show the Radical Left that we are not letting up—noteven for a second. If you have anything left in the tank to give, please sendit in before midnight tonight and it will go DIRECTLY towards our final voteroutreach operation. SEND A FINAL SURGE OF SUPPORT Thank you in advance foryour generosity and action in these final days—it’s because of YOU that wewill win big on November 5th and get back to winning for the great people ofNew Jersey and America. Let’s do this. –Team Kean Paid for by Kean forCongress Inc Copyright © 2024 Kean for Congress Our mailing address is: Keanfor Congress Inc PO Box 999 Edison, NJ 08818 Click here to mail yourdonation. If you would like to donate online, please visit our website here .Be sure to follow the campaign on Facebook , Instagram , Twitter , and YouTube. If you have any suggestions, comments, complaints, or feedback, please sendyour ideas toinfo@TomKean.com . Click here to unsubscribe
